{start_of_verse: Verse 1}
[C]Wide awake and feeling mortal
[G7]At this moment in the dream
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_verse: Verse 2}
That old man there in the mirror
[C]And my shaky self-esteem
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_verse: Verse 3}
Here today and gone tomorrow
[F]Is the way it's gotta be
[C]With an empty blue horizon
[G7]For as far as I can [C]see
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_verse: Verse 4}
[F]God Almighty here I am
[C]Am I where I oughta be
[G7]I've begun to soon descend
[C]Like the sun into the sea
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_verse: Verse 5}
[F]And I thank my lucky stars
[C]From here to eternity
[G7]For the artist that You are
[C]And the man You made of me
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_verse: Verse 6}
Pretty speeches still unspoken
[G7]Perfect circles in the sand
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_verse: Verse 7}
Rules and promises I've broken
[C]That I still don't understand
{end_of_verse}






